{
  "text": "In order to measure the volumetric errors at the tool center point \u03b4\u03c4 , a non-contact measuring instrument, called CapBall, had been developed in house [CITATION_1] . It consists in a master ball mounted on the table and a sensing head fitted with three capacitive sensors, mounted in a tool holder in the spindle.",
